data.title: ultimateParentCode
data.text:
Container that represents the ultimate parent code for the company. If a value appears for this element, this indicates that the current company is a child, or subsidiary of a parent company. For example, if you search on Compaq Computer Corporation, the ultimate parent is Hewlett-Packard Corporation.

A company can have between zero and an unlimited number of <ultimateParentCode> elements.
